'''Razor trees''' were a type of tree indigenous to [[Baskarn]]. They had razor-sharp leaves and limbs that functioned to deter herbivores and to saw off the limbs of other trees that grew too close. The [[Yrashu]] were the only beings who knew how to climb these trees properly.

